Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> and so it's like every day I'm\Ncommitting mental and emotional suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and not and choosing that as opposed to\N>> how does one
