Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The addiction to things that are\Nnegative is because of the payoff we get
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,out of them. The hardest one is being\Nvictim, being martyr, being right. Each
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,one of those has a payoff. So the\Nquestion is not am I willing to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,being right or am I willing to give up\Nbeing the martyr. The question is am I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,willing to get to to surrender to God\Nthe payoff I get out of that
