Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to surrender to\Neverything everything to God
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,even the pain of being the victim and\Nbeing wronged etc. Sooner or later you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,have to let it go.\NI had people ask me questions couple
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,months ago someplace and she was asking\Nme about something that you know is over
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,already 20 years ago but I can tell\Nshe's clinging to it still trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,juice it trying to juice some kind of an\Ninjustice you see and I said haven't you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,noticed that what you're talking about\Nis already at the top of every single a
