Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,energy of those emotions.\NDoesn't have its own emotion. It has to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,extract it human life. Yeah.\NI'm going to teach a course um starting
