Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Well, let's see.\NIf you take Fortune magazine and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate all the\Nall the businesses in it, you'll find
