Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.48,0:24:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that 24 hours a day, 7 days a week\Nbecause that's what he was and that's
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.44,0:24:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what he did. So he would he was trying\Nto set an example and show by
