Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.52,0:25:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,People hate the successful. So, we envy\Nsuccess and we hate it and seek to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.00,0:25:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,destroy it.\NIt depends on what you mean by
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.20,0:25:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,leadership. You mean specific\Nleadership? Do you mean by example,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.40,0:25:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,by inspiration? To me, leadership is\Nthe one who inspires and by their
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.72,0:25:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,inspiration recontextualizes the entire\Nenterprise and uplifts everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.36,0:25:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where your chief of staff, your the\Nfunction you serve is the focus of the
