Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.15,0:26:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,his cigar God bless him he smoked we\Nwon't miss it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.03,0:26:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so the various aspects of leadership are\Nmultitudinous you see
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.15,0:26:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,>> these people are peace and justice\Npeople and they wouldn't want to hear
