Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.64,0:27:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see since we went from 190 to\N207, you see that which is non-integrous
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.64,0:27:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,falling left and right. heads of all the\NCEOs of the big corporations,
