Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.32,0:27:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,new paradigm of success and true\Nleadership is integrity. integrity to
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.96,0:27:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,your company, to your fellow worker, to\Nyourself,
