Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.52,0:28:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The people here are poor. It's crap all\Nover the street. Dog poo, garbage,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.44,0:28:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,newspaper.\NThey say, "Well, they don't get the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.76,0:29:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,right education." No, that's not at all.\NThe field, the field, the broken window,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.79,0:29:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the broken window theory explains it.\NThe field is down and everything that
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.91,0:29:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,comes into the field is attracted by the\Ndownness of the field. And the behaviors
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.79,0:29:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,within that field are one of abuse of\Nchildren, abuse of responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.52,0:29:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,drugs, addiction, crime, devastation,\Ninconsideration for others, rudeness,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.84,0:29:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,confrontationalism.\NThe raising of the level of
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.60,0:29:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness then is what you can do\Nfor the poor. Giving them money makes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.44,0:29:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,them worse.\N>> Well, I think you just made my job
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.03,0:29:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,harder.\N>> Giving people poor the poor money makes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.79,0:29:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,them worse. They saw that in Haiti. The\Nmore money a poor poured into Haiti, the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.15,0:29:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,worse it got. Uh it's because that is\Nnot the cause. That is the consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.76,0:29:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's mixing up cause and effect.\NSee, poverty is the consequence of a
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.79,0:30:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,certain level of consciousness which is\Nnot integrous, which only thinks in
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.12,0:30:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,terms of me and goes out of the solar\Nplexus animal wise. When you're in a
