Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.96,0:30:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know from the footstep to cross\Nover and go this way. That's why I live
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.27,0:30:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell the tale.\NYou live by animal instinct,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.24,0:30:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,not by intelligence, not by education.\NYour animal instinct is what tells you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.24,0:30:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,whether this elevator is safe to take it\Nor not. Whether this floor is safe to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.03,0:31:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,get off, the door opens. You see what's\Nout there
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.03,0:31:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,at 4 in the morning and you push the\Nelevator, you know, the door opens and
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.55,0:31:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,here's six big guys looking at me like\Nand I looked at it and I went and we all
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.36,0:31:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed. until y'all left. I saw what\Nthey were. They saw that I saw what they
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.55,0:31:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,were and it was all okay with us. It's\Nokay with me if you want to mug people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.96,0:31:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm not a moralist. You see,\Nit's just that I don't want to be the
