Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.32,0:31:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,was no contest. So, it was okay with me\Nif they won. They intimidated me, which
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.67,0:31:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is fine. I said, I am intimidated. Why?\NSo in terms of what I tell these people,
