Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.24,0:32:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Exhibits caringness about others.\N>> Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.79,0:32:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,>> And then it may ignite or may not\Nignite. But that you can't do it for the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.67,0:32:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,effect. You have to do it because that's\Nwhat you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.24,0:32:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Okay?\N>> So the person goes into a community like
