Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.24,0:32:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,effect. That's seeing yourself as cause\Nand effect. No, it's what you are that
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.20,0:32:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,radiates out.\NSo you become that which you wish others
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.08,0:32:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to become like and you do that by being\Nthat yourself because that's what you
